Templates for iReport
-------------------------

0.) Prerequisites

	You need a running Icinga with IDO

	If there's something missing on your system, please refer to the Icinga
	documentation website:

    		http://docs.icinga.org/

	For using the templates you need a running iReport. Download and a installtion
	guide cann you find on the website:

		http://jasperforge.org/projects/ireport


1.) Installation

	Copy the templates in the template folder to your iReport installation. As example:

		~/icinga-reports/ireport/templates/1.6 $ cp -r * /opt/iReport-4.1.3/ireport/templates/.


2.) Using templates

	Open iReport and select "File -> New". In the Wizard select "Report" and select a Icinga report.
	Now you can begin to create your own Icinga report.


	Have fun!
